      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and practicality, whether as a starter vehicle, commuter, or project. A straightforward opportunity to own a vehicle at a very attractive price.",
