      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants cheap transport, a handy backup car, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s priced to be approachable, and I\u2019m happy to be straightforward about it so there are no surprises. If you want something honest, usable, and easy on the wallet, this could be a great fit.",
