      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with plenty of character. Runs, drives, and offers a strong mechanical foundation for someone looking for an affordable commuter, weekend project, or parts-savvy buy. The powertrain feels willing, the chassis is straightforward, and it has the kind of usable, no-frills appeal that makes it easy to live with and improve over time. Cosmetics and overall condition reflect age and wear, but for the right buyer this is a practical entry-point car with real potential. Priced to move and well-suited for someone who values function over flash.",
      "price": 5950.0,
